    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Intraco Penta Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, distributes heavy equipment and spare parts in Indonesia. It operates through Sale of Heavy Equipment and Spare Parts; Maintenance, Mining and Rental Service; Manufacturing; and Others segments. The company distributes construction and commercial transportation equipment, heavy trucks, portable air compressors, and lighting sources; leases and repairs heavy equipment; and provides after-sales services. It also offers mining contracting solutions, such as application and maintenance of mining equipment, mining exploration, mine planning, infrastructure development, mining exploitation, and reforestation services. In addition, the company provides fabrication and infrastructure support services for various sectors comprising the mining, industrial, oil and gas, marine, and logistics sectors; financing services; and operates a steam power plant as an independent power producer. Further, it is involved in the repair and maintenance of cars and motorbikes; processing industry; travel agents and other business support; workshop and manufacturing; trading and rental activities; and plantation, transportation, construction, infrastructure, real estate, and printing activities. The company operates in Kalimantan, Jakarta, Sumatera, Java, and other areas. PT Intraco Penta Tbk was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.",
